---
title: Get started with Solidus
description: Solidus is an open source ecommerce solution built with Ruby on Rails and maintained by a community of passionate developers.
---

<div class="get-started-hero hero-block content-block">
  <div class="container container-md text-center">
    <h1 class="title">Get started <span class="d-block">with <span>Solidus</span></span></h1>
    <p class="lead mb-md-6">
      Solidus is an open source ecommerce solution built with Ruby on Rails and maintained by a community of passionate developers.
    </p>
    <div class="btn-group get-started__anchor-links">
      <a href="#developers" class="">For Developers</a>
      <a href="#non-developers" class="">For Non-developers</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="content-block content-block-gray-900">
  <div class="container container-md content-block pt-0 text-center" id="developers">
    <h5 class="text-success">For Developers</h5>
    <h2>A truly open-source <span class="d-lg-block">mindset</span></h2>
    <p class="lead">Solidus is created by a dedicated group of passionate developers, agencies and retailers that work together to move the platform forward.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="container get-started-developers">
    <div class="row align-items-center get-started-developers__step">
      <div class="col-md-5 get-started-developers__step__image mb-4 mb-md-0">
        <img data-srcset="<%= image_path('illustrations/get-started_terminal@2x.png') %> 2x, <%= image_path('illustrations/get-started_terminal@1x.png') %> 1x" class="img-fluid" alt="Install Solidus" width="100%" >
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-5 ml-md-auto">
        <h4>Install Solidus</h4>
        <p>If you have an existing Ruby on Rails application, installing Solidus is fairly simple.</p>
        <a href="https://github.com/login?return_to=%2Fsolidusio%2Fsolidus" target="blank" class="btn btn-primary"><%= inline_svg("social-icons/github.svg", class: "isvg") %> Fork Solidus</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row align-items-center get-started-developers__step">
      <div class="col-md-5 get-started-developers__step__image mb-4 mb-md-0">
        <img data-srcset="<%= image_path('illustrations/get-started_browser@2x.png') %> 2x, <%= image_path('illustrations/get-started_browser@1x.png') %> 1x" class="img-fluid" alt="Build your storefront" width="100%" >
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-5 ml-md-auto">
        <h4>Build your storefront</h4>
        <p>If you have an existing Ruby on Rails application, installing Solidus is fairly simple.</p>
        <a href="/extensions" class="get-started-link">See all the extensions</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row align-items-center get-started-developers__step">
      <div class="col-md-5 get-started-developers__step__image mb-4 mb-md-0">
        <img data-srcset="<%= image_path('illustrations/get-started_guides@2x.png') %> 2x, <%= image_path('illustrations/get-started_guides@1x.png') %> 1x" class="img-fluid" alt="Learn Solidus" width="100%" >
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-5 ml-md-auto">
        <h4>Learn Solidus</h4>
        <p>Solidus Guides provide a foundation for web developers to learn the Solidus ecommerce platform. Use it while you build out your Solidus store.</p>
        <a href="https://guides.solidus.io/developers/" target="_blank" class="get-started-link">Read our guides</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row align-items-center get-started-developers__step">
      <div class="col-md-5 get-started-developers__step__image mb-4 mb-md-0">
        <img data-srcset="<%= image_path('illustrations/get-started_support@2x.png') %> 2x, <%= image_path('illustrations/get-started_support@1x.png') %> 1x" class="img-fluid" alt="Solidus support" width="100%" >
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-5 ml-md-auto">
        <h4>Get help</h4>
        <p>Get help from our community. Stay connected with developers, stakeholders and experts all around the world.</p>
        <a href="http://slack.solidus.io/" target="_blank" class="get-started-link">Join our Slack</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="content-block">
  <div class="container container-md content-block pt-0 text-center" id="non-developers">
    <h5 class="text-primary">For Non-developers</h5>
    <h2>Yours to customize, <span class="d-lg-block">yours forever.</span></h2>
    <p class="lead">Free your business from useless limitations. Solidus gives you the freedom to change and iterate as much as you want. Start small, grow big: discover what moves the needle for your brand and make it happen.</p>
  </div>

